      "writtenOn": "2020-10-22T13:19:45Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "It seems really awkward to pass in this bug tracker specific config as part of the generic interface and then fail if it\u0027s not the right type.\n\nWouldn\u0027t it be better to pass in the GitHubQueryConfig via New, store it in the instance, and keep it out of the interface?",
