        "id": 5145
      },
      "writtenOn": "2020-10-22T18:03:58Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Agree that it is awkward. I had originally thought about adding it to Init/New but then could not have just one instance of each bug framework.\nPassing it in Search makes it possible to reuse the same bug framework instance for different queries. For example, all the monorail queries done in the poller: https://skia-review.googlesource.com/c/buildbot/+/329077/1/bugs-central/go/bugs/poller.go#158",
